metadata.name: FalconRocket #2
metadata.description:
The Falcon fleet NFT collection grants access to our revolutionary Falcon moonpad for innovative blockchain projects! You get the opportunity to be a part of the next big thing in the world of crypto. The Launchpad is not just a platform for token sales, but a comprehensive ecosystem that provides support and guidance to emerging projects.

One of the unique features of Falcon $Fleet is the vetting committee that ensures the projects onboarded meet our high standards of quality and potential for success. As a presale participant, you will have access to this committee and the opportunity to contribute your expertise and insights to the evaluation process.

We offer referral rewards to our NFT holders and community members who bring promising projects to our attention. By spreading the word about Falcon MoonPad, you not only help us discover new and exciting projects, but you also earn rewards for your contributions.

Join us on this journey towards a more innovative and decentralized future. Get ready to be a part of something big with your Falcon $Fleet NFT!
